HEADWORD: Paguma
<hw>Pa*gu"ma</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of several species of East Indian viverrine mammals of the
genus <gen>Paguma</gen>. They resemble a weasel in form.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

